## 6. How Competitors Solve This

*   **Sprii.io (Social Commerce Specialist):** Focuses heavily on direct Meta integrations. They default to mobile app camera streams and use direct checkout page routing via Shopify draft orders, with typo-tolerant keyword matching. They lack advanced multi-platform broadcasting setups.
*   **Restream / StreamYard (Video Specialist):** Excellent video routers (using SRS-like pipelines and FFmpeg duplication). They do not offer deep e-commerce sync, comment-to-buy parsers, or cart checkout automation.
*   **Livescale (Brand Storefront Specialist):** Embeds an interactive player on the merchant's website, rendering clickable HTML shop cards over the stream. They do not offer automated comment-to-buy DM checkouts on social platforms.